## How add chatbot on Website
- Click on chat trigger to get 'Chat url'
- Add the code below on your website:
```html
<script type="module">
        import { createChat } from 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@n8n/chat/dist/chat.bundle.es.js';

        createChat({
            webhookUrl: "chat_url_value_here"
        });
    </script>   
```

